pr_title: Google Summer of Code 2020: Build Integration and Badges
pr_body:
~This PR is a work in progress. Its purpose is to view and get suggestions on the GSoC-2020 work and it is **not** supposed to be merged at the moment.
I will keep updating this PR and it can be merged at the end.~

This PR is now completed and it can be merged.
Major Changes
1. Coverage report and Test status are now available.
2. Maintainers can now trigger a rebuild of a package.
3. Above features are available for candidate packages as well.
4. Added Badges to Packages' homepage
5. New Flag to rebuild packages previously built with an older GHC version.

In-depth details about changes can be found in the below link.
https://gist.github.com/awasthishubh/2076e6d297c953869ac13bc223e5017d
